translation.Name: Buak_Note_48
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Now that the team finally pulled themselves together, I was able to get the report on what happened.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_3: After she died during one of the procedures, the orders were simple. Incinerate the body.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_4: While those slackers were grieving for that monster instead of doing their job, something happened.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_5: She resurrected, after all these years, all those experiments, all the money that went into this.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_6: All of that and sheâ€™s the one who gets to come back? What a joke.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_7: And to the team who thought they could fix her? I told you, look at you now.
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_8: I should have listened to my gut and put her down years ago.
